text.tspan: Wind energy generation vs. installed capacity, 2000 to 2022
Wind energy generation, measured in gigawatt-hours (GWh) versus cumulative installed wind energy capacity,
measured in gigawatts (GW). Data includes energy from both onshore and offshore wind sources.
Data source: Energy Institute - Statistical Review of World Energy (2023); International Renewable Energy Agency (2023)
